FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://glmarous.me/

# glamrous.me

Glamrous has a simple API that lets you get information on all your favorite makeup items.

## Products Collection [/product{?limit}]

+ Parameters
    + limit (number, optional) - max number of products to list. -1 means all.

