### Create a New Brand [POST]

You may create your own brand using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing the name of the brand and a link to it's image
and returns a JSON object about the product added including it's 
assigned id and some initialized values.

+ Request (application/json)

        [
            {
                "brand_id": 1,
                "brand_name": "Pure Anada", 
                "image_link": "https://d3t32hsnjxo7q6.cloudfront.net/i/afefede002b8d94f6e53ea07dd4070f9_ra,w158,h184_pa,w158,h184.jpg"
            }
        ]
        ]

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /brand/1

    + Body

              {
                "brand_id": 1,
                "brand_name": "Pure Anada", 
                "avg_price": 0.0,
                "avg_rating": 0.0,
                "num_products": 0,
                "image_link": "https://d3t32hsnjxo7q6.cloudfront.net/i/afefede002b8d94f6e53ea07dd4070f9_ra,w158,h184_pa,w158,h184.jpg"
            }
            
